dc_description_s: Map shows populated areas, shantytowns, roads, cemeteries, and notable features. Includes city location map, boundaries diagram, and glossary. "This sheet falls within NA 38-1, 1501, 1:250,000 and NA 38-03, Y630, 1:100,000." "NSN 7643014033642." "NIMA ref. no. Y921WAAJID." "Printed by DMAHTC 12-92." "Reprinted by NIMA 6-01." "This map is red-light readable." "A lane is considered as being a minimum of 2.5 meters in width. Normal railroad gauge is 1.44 meters (4ʹ8.5ʹʹ)." "Caution: This product may not conform to the horizontal accuracy requirements. Extreme caution should be used when making measurements." ©Copyright 1992 by the United States Government.
